description: Beneath a pink stucco ceiling, a bundle of dried flowers hangs on one of the honey gold oak walls.  A lacquered wooden shelf and a low wrought iron table sit in opposite corners while a knotted woolen rug rests on a honey gold oak floor.

A bundle of dried flowers hangs on one of the honey gold oak walls, and a pink stucco ceiling rises overhead.  A knotted woolen rug sits in one corner of a honey gold oak floor.  There is a lacquered wooden shelf on one side of the shop and a low wrought iron table on the other.
